    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of ox-like grazing hooved animals native to North America; sometimes divided into subspecies based on their habitat: the plains bison and woodland bison.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
